                    <span>This book is a perfect choice for those of us interested in all things coffee - from roasting to buying to grinding to growing and lots in-between. Kenneth Davids's book is informative, honest, and humorous.  Includes places to purchase coffee and coffee supplies, an extensive coffee  glossary, helpful illustrations and tables, and so much more. A great book.</span>
                  
              
